name: Rancor
Lore: 'Indigenous to Dathomir, but found on several dozen worlds throughout the galaxy. Vicious predator. Sometimes kept as pets by eccentrics and crime lords.',
Text: '* Ferocity = 8 + destiny. Habitat: Rancor Pit and exterior planet sites. Deploys only to the rancor pit or to where Malakili is the only character. Moves towards another Rancor whenever possible.',
